{"tid":1775303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"80萬係長駐人數，200萬係最大人數","createTime":"2019-12-08T18:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T21:30:35.000Z","uid":318701,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0f2df8ee1e1e67cbb50d7c735200f48a33d60d","tid":1775303,"uid":318701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"回帶去半年前<br />\n點解616會有咁多人上街？<br />\n送中近了，警暴來了，末日快到了<br />\n梗係死都死出嚟啦<br />\n咪「逼」咗200萬人出嚟囉<br />\n<br />\n而家呢？<br />\n有人權法，有區選大勝加持，送中收皮了，民意都明顯冇變過<br />\n即係冇deadline，正處於平穩期<br />\n換言之今日只係平常嘅日子<br />\n然後有80萬人「自願」出咗嚟<br />\n<br />\n所以80萬真係好多，唔好下下畀200萬限制自己嘅思考"},{"pid":"078c2737bd1659299017c3184e5af560f84632e1","tid":1775303,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"Correct ah push"},{"pid":"68dc833547fc102bfd972662ba6018e66aff7a6a","tid":1775303,"uid":129044,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T19:10:13.000Z","msg":"真 616個日印象中係吹咗成個星期雞（唔知有冇記錯）<br />\n128係星期三定四先有不反 個陣班狗又冇咁猖狂<br />\n仲要狗影都冇隻 唔會話做埋d on9野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明80萬已經係好撚大嘅數字 睇下其他國家嘅政府？跪咗啦屌 係港共先咁無恥咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c97ec8cf7caaafa525af0af17ce88d68b379566","tid":1775303,"uid":269515,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T19:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfor3kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftfor3kb.jpg&h=3bdf14ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMKVWE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMKVWE8.jpg&h=ef7e3361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSvh9Z7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSvh9Z7.jpg&h=1e87f419&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b5b994eab19995509e88669d6dd20fc5bcface3","